regular_eggs.name: Violet Egg
regular_eggs.description: Garth's Favorite Color. He grows violet flowers because of how pretty they are. He loves the smell of them around his house too.

regular_eggs.name: Rainbow Egg
regular_eggs.description: Whitney's Favorite Color. Her personality shines bright with this egg as she loves to express herself.

regular_eggs.name: Green Egg
regular_eggs.description: Ezaf's Favorite Color. It represents his passion for nature and the wilderness. He commonly visits the ethereal gardens.

regular_eggs.name: Yellow Egg
regular_eggs.description: Zilra's Favorite Color. Every morning she gets up just to watch the beautiful sunrise and watch the colors unfold in her eyes.

regular_eggs.name: Blue Egg
regular_eggs.description: Hollis's Favorite Color. Born with a unique talent of being able to swim swiftly and cunningly. He commonly visits the Oracle Rivers.

regular_eggs.name: Snowy Egg
regular_eggs.description: Fausta's Favorite Color. The color of protein in eggs which she eats regularly to keeps up her already impressive physique.

regular_eggs.name: Dark Egg
regular_eggs.description: Hini's Favorite Color. Often known for burning food he cooks, even though it is his favorite way of cooking for some reason.

regular_eggs.name: Red Egg
regular_eggs.description: Otger's Favorite Color. Red usually helps him realize how much he needs to work on his anger.

regular_eggs.name: Orange Egg
regular_eggs.description: Julie's Favorite Color. Often, Julie likes to snack on fruit or veggies, most commonly oranges and carrots.

regular_eggs.name: Purple Egg
regular_eggs.description: Hakon's Favorite Color. The symbol of Arcane Energy. His fascination with it proves to be his downfall as he cannot weld such power. He commonly visits the crimson grove.

regular_eggs.name: Gold Egg
regular_eggs.description: Wolter's Favorite Color. Gifted gold by his very king, he treasures it with his life as it shows a symbol of trust and honor for him and his own kind.

regular_eggs.name: Honey Zebra Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Honey Zebra is faster than your typical Zebra. Some have also said the meat tastes sweeter.

regular_eggs.name: Grass Zebra Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Grass Zebras green coat allow them to hide better from predators.

regular_eggs.name: Cookies n Cream Zebra Egg
regular_eggs.description: The iconic pattern resembles a normal zebra but this one has a twist. If the zebra is left in the sun way too long it starts to melt. The conoras are still unable to figure out why.

regular_eggs.name: Lava Zebra Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Lava Zebra can withstand hot temperatures and even stand in fire. Their skin is also so hot that it can easily melt the touch of others.

regular_eggs.name: Iced Zebra Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Iced Zebras can withstand cold temperatures. They also feel more comfortable in the north of the Ethereal Gardens.

regular_eggs.name: Crimson Tiger Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Crimson Zebras are a manifestation of arcane power and they are not truly a zebra, even though it does act like one. Unlike the crimson wizard, they do not wish to harm others and prefer to live peacefully.

regular_eggs.name: Golden Tiger Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Golden Tigers represent leadership and growth. They often lead packs to help to battles or new homes.

regular_eggs.name: Mossy Tiger Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Mossy Tigers are the masters of hunting as they can blend in easily with their skin. Every day, they bring their own weight in food for the rest of their kin.

regular_eggs.name: Wild Tiger Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Wild Tigers are very ferocious creatures that often live alone. Their formidable strength can outweigh five others.

regular_eggs.name: Instinct Tiger Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Instinct Tigers are masters of wit and strategy. They provide the golden tigers knowledge to command, conquer and survive.

regular_eggs.name: Leafed Reptile Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Leafed Reptiles have very Fragile Skin that can be rip apart by the very winds. Due to this condition, they are endangered. However, the conoras make sure they have a safe home on the Ethereal Gardens by keeping them on the grand tree.

regular_eggs.name: Ripe Reptile Egg
regular_eggs.description: The Ripe Reptile's Life Cycle is kind of unusual.
